---
layout: base.njk
title: NOWA Virtual 5k Walk & Fun Run - Full Supply
description: >-
  Your Race Participation, Donation or Sponsorship Can Change a Life. No One Has
  to Walk Alone. Our 5th annual Virtual 5k “No One Walks Alone,” also known as
  NOWA, is something we strongly believe.
pageCss: true
---
{% from "components/macros.njk" import button, section, sectionHead, hero, ctaBand, card, cardGrid %}

{% set paypalUrl = "https://www.paypal.com/donate?hosted_button_id=YM6KWR6J5EM2L&source=url" %}
{% set registerUrl = "https://runsignup.com/Race/Register/?raceId=124629" %}
{% set scheduleUrl = "https://sfkakxvwfuajznbsmu.10to8.com/" %}
{% set sponsorPacketUrl = "/assets/docs/nowa-5k-sponsor-levels-benefits-packet-2026.pdf" %}

{# ===================== HERO ===================== #}
{% set heroTitle %}<img class="nowa-hero__logo" src="{{ '/assets/img/nowa-logo.png' | url }}" alt="No One Walks Alone" /><span class="nowa-hero__text">Your Race Participation, Donation or Sponsorship Can Change a Life.</span>{% endset %}
{% call hero(
  heroTitle,
  bgImage=("/assets/img/nowa-5k-hero.jpg" | url),
  overlay="light"
) %}
  {{ button("Donate", paypalUrl, variant="donate", attrs='target="_blank" rel="noopener"') }}
{% endcall %}

{# ===================== NO ONE HAS TO WALK ALONE ===================== #}
{% call section() %}
  <h2 class="nowa-heading">No One Has to Walk Alone</h2>
  <div class="nowa-intro">
    <div class="nowa-intro__body">
      <p>Our 5th annual Virtual 5k &ldquo;No One Walks Alone,&rdquo; also known as NOWA, is something we strongly believe. Many Christian women are seeking a mentor, but they do not know who to ask or where to find one. That&rsquo;s why Full Supply trains leaders who transforms lives for Christ in the U.S. Russia, India and Africa.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="nowa-intro__media">
      <img src="{{ '/assets/img/nowa-nadia-natasha-arthur.jpg' | url }}" alt="" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
  </div>
{% endcall %}

{# ===================== JOIN OUR 5TH ANNUAL VIRTUAL 5K ===================== #}
{% call section(size="tight") %}
  <h2 class="nowa-join__title">Join our 5th Annual Virtual<br />5k Walk/Fun Run</h2>
{% endcall %}

{# ===================== WALK OR RUN WITH US ===================== #}
{% call section(tone="alt") %}
  <div class="nowa-walkrun">
    <div class="nowa-walkrun__media">
      <img src="{{ '/assets/img/nowa-5k-runners.jpg' | url }}" alt="" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
    <div class="nowa-walkrun__body">
      <h2 class="nowa-heading nowa-heading--left">Walk or Run with us to Transform Lives</h2>
      <p>Take your Virtual 5k Walk or Fun Run in your neighborhood, at a local park or on your treadmill. You choose when &amp; where you walk between October 2nd starting at 6:00 a.m. and October 18th ending at 11:59 p.m.</p>
      <p>Track your time on an app of your choice. Then be sure to log it on the event website on or before October 20th by 11:59 p.m.</p>
      <p>{{ button("Register for 5k", registerUrl, variant="accent", attrs='target="_blank" rel="noopener"') }}</p>
    </div>
  </div>
{% endcall %}

{# ===================== OUR CURRENT SPONSORS ===================== #}
{% call section(tone="alt") %}
  {{ sectionHead("Our Current Sponsors", center=true) }}
  <div class="nowa-sponsors">
    <div class="nowa-sponsors__logo"><img src="{{ '/assets/img/sponsor-maxwell-house.png' | url }}" alt="Maxwell House" loading="lazy" /></div>
    <div class="nowa-sponsors__logo"><img src="{{ '/assets/img/sponsor-mellow-mushroom.png' | url }}" alt="Mellow Mushroom" loading="lazy" /></div>
    <div class="nowa-sponsors__logo"><img src="{{ '/assets/img/sponsor-kfc.png' | url }}" alt="KFC" loading="lazy" /></div>
  </div>
{% endcall %}

{# ===================== WE ARE SEEKING MORE SPONSORS ===================== #}
<section class="nowa-band" style="background-image:url('{{ '/assets/img/nowa-5k-walk-run-band.jpg' | url }}')">
  <div class="nowa-band__overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="nowa-band__title">We Are Seeking MORE Sponsors to Join Our Cause</h2>
  </div>
</section>

